Usage: start_parallel_edit [-help] [-area_restricted] -region {x1 y1 x2 y2}

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
-area_restricted          # Only capture difference inside or touch edit area.
                          # (bool, optional)
-region {x1 y1 x2 y2}     # Specifies the square to indicate the edit area.
                          # (box, required)